UNION ALL
SELECT C.[ParentProductCategoryID], C.[ProductCategoryID], C.[Name] FROM SalesLT.ProductCategory AS C INNER JOIN CategoryCTE AS BC ON BC.ProductCategoryID = C.ParentProductCategoryID )
